e juntan, estos se fusionan y crean nuevos tipos de Chompis","N1D10-Eng","New Chompis to discover!","N1D10-Esp","¡Nuevos Chompis para descubrir!","N1D11-Eng","My friend Paco is excited about these new monsters, but he doesn't know how to help the Chompis.","N1D11-Esp","Mi amigo Paco se emociona con estos nuevos monstruos, pero no sabe cómo ayudar a los Chompis.","N1D12-Eng","Apparently when two groups of Chompis get together, they act as an addition or subtraction of numbers.","N1D12-Esp","Al parecer cuando dos grupos de Chompis se juntan, estos actúan como una suma o una resta de números.","N1D13-Eng","Each Chompi has a value in its bellies, the value of each Chompi will be added or subtracted depending on the case.","N1D13-Esp","Cada Chompi tiene un valor en sus panzas, el valor de cada Chompi será sumado o restado según el caso.","N1D14-Eng","That sounds complicated.","N1D14-Esp","Eso suena complicado.","N1D15-Eng","Don't worry! I will help you, and I am sure that you will help us too.","N1D15-Esp","¡No te preocupes! Yo te ayudaré, y estoy segura que tú también nos vas a ayudar.","N1D16-Eng","Please help me with these amazing creatures.","N1D16-Esp","Por favor, ayúdame con estas asombrosas criaturas.","N1D17-Eng","Well, let's start with the simplest thing, the sum of Chompis.","N1D17-Esp","Bien, empezemos con lo más sencillo, la suma de Chompis.","N1D18-Eng","We will give you two groups of three Chompis. You must click on each block as shown here.","N1D18-Esp","Te daremos dos grupos de tres Chompis. Deberás darle click a cada bloque como aquí se muestra.","N1D19-Eng","This will separate the group and make it easier to add the values ​​of each Chompi.","N1D19-Esp","Esto hará que se separe el grupo y sea más sencillo el sumar los valores de cada Chompi.","N1D20-Eng","Since Chompis have values ​​from 0 to 9, values ​​that add up to 10 or more will be separated.","N1D20-Esp","Cómo los Chompis tienen valores del 0 al 9, valores que sumen 10 o más serán separados.","N1D21-Eng","For example, if the answer is 12, the value will be divided into 1 and 2. The 1 will be added for the next block, the 2 will remain in the result.","N1D21-Esp","Por ejemplo, si la respuesta es 12, el valor será dividido en 1 y 2. El 1 se sumará para el siguiente bloque, el 2 se quedará en el resultado.","N1D22-Eng","When you finish all the blocks...","N1D22-Esp","Cuando acabes con todos los bloques...","N1D23-Eng","KABOOM! All the Chompis get together and will give a new group of Chompis!","N1D23-Esp","¡KABOOM! ¡Todos los Chompis se juntan y darán un nuevo grupo de Chompis!","N1D24-Eng","I want you to meet these monsters! Get ready!","N1D24-Esp","¡Ya quiero que conozcas estos monstruos! ¡Preparate!","N1D25-Eng","Calm down, good luck with this task, I know you can solve it","N1D25-Esp","Con calma, suerte en esta tarea, sé que podrás resolverlo","N1D26-Eng","We both trust you!","N1D26-Esp","¡Ambos confiamos en tí!","N2D1-Eng","Congratulations on finishing the previous test! I knew you could do it.","N2D1-Esp","¡Felicidades por haber terminado la anterior prueba! Sabía que podrías lograrlo.","N2D2-Eng","The Chompis are very happy with your performance, thank you very much!","N2D2-Esp","Los Chompis están muy contentos por tu desempeño, ¡muchas gracias!","N2D3-Eng","However, this is not over yet","N2D3-Esp","Sin embargo, esto aún no ha terminado","N2D4-Eng","Hang in there, the new mission is coming!","N2D4-Esp","¡Aguanta las ansias que ahí viene la nueva misión!","N2D5-Eng","Hang in there, the new mission is coming!","N2D5-Esp","¡Aguanta las ansias que ahí viene la nueva misión!","N2D6-Eng","Now we will do the operations for the subtractions","N2D6-Esp","Ahora haremos las operaciones para las restas","N2D7-Eng","For this we will do the same as when we added, divide into blocks to make it easier to subtract.","N2D7-Esp","Para esto haremos lo mismo que cuando sumabamos, dividir en bloques para que sea más sencillo restar.","N2D8-Eng","Wait, but what if the top number is less than the bottom number?","N2D8-Esp","Espera, pero ¿si el número de arriba es menor que el de abajo?","N2D9-Eng","Good observation! If this happens, the number above, which is called the minuend, will be added a 1.","N2D9-Esp","¡Buena observación! Si esto pasa, el número de arriba, el cuál se llama minuendo, se le agregará un 1.","N2D10-Eng","This is not a 1 as such, if you notice the monster is different. This is why you are actually adding 10 to the current value.","N2D10-Esp","Esto no es un 1 como tal, si notas el monstruo es distinto. Esto es por qué en realidad se le está sumando 10 al valor actual.","N2D11-Eng","In this case, our subtraction goes from 1-4 to 11-4.","N2D11-Esp","En este caso, nuestra resta pasa de ser 1-4 a 11-4.","N2D12-Eng","That will make things easier, but what will happen to that number?","N2D12-Esp","Eso hará las cosas más sencillas, pero, ¿qué pasará con ese número?","N2D13-Eng","When the operation is finished, it is subtracted from the next block, due to the previous operation.","N2D13-Esp","Cuando la operación se termina, se le resta al siguiente bloque, esto debido a la anterior operación.","N2D14-Eng","Well then we are ready!","N2D14-Esp","¡Bueno entonces ya estamos listos!","N2D15-Eng","Perfect! In that case, let's go!","N2D15-Esp","¡Perfecto! En ese caso, ¡vamos allá!","N3D1-Eng","Seriously, you are amazing!","N3D1-Esp","¡Enserio, eres increíble!","N3D2-Eng","Thank you very much for your help, now the Chompis are very happy...","N3D2-Esp","Muchas gracias por tu ayuda, ahora los Chompis están muy contentos...","N3D3-Eng","...","N3D3-Esp","...","N3D4-Eng","Wait...what's going on?","N3D4-Esp","Espera... ¿qué pasa?","N3D5-Eng","I think it will rain...","N3D5-Esp","Creo que lloverá...","N3D6-Eng","It's not rain...","N3D6-Esp","No es lluvia...","N3D7-Eng","They are Chompis!","N3D7-Esp","¡Son Chompis!","N3D8-Eng","Hahaha, a whole avalanche of them!","N3D8-Esp","Jajaja, ¡toda una avalancha de ellos!","N3D9-Eng","Hahaha, apparen